<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/jun/04/">&#x27a0;</a> June 4, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="bill-simmons-its-hard-say-good" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://sports.espn.go.com/espnmag/story?id=4223584">Bill Simmons - It&#39;s hard to say goodbye to David Ortiz</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Great piece by Bill Simmons on the decline of the Large Father. FWIW, I don&#8217;t think Papi&#8217;s current decline is a sign of stopping using a banned substance &#8212; Why would he stop now? Nothing has changed in MLB testing over the last couple of years.</p>

