<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>AT&T Park</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2896622863/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="AT&T Park" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3196/2896622863_c162a2f41d_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Ever since I first saw the Red Sox on TV playing at &quot;SBC Park&quot; (as then was), I've thought the Giants' park was gorgeous.  This afternoon, Joy &amp; I went to see their season closer against LA, and it was as lovely as I'd hoped.</p>

<p>Large, but intimate, and right next to the Pacific, I dream of the day the Red Sox ditch Fenway and build something as special as AT&amp;T Park.</p>
        </p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
